# pnpm configuration
# ===================

# Hoist Sentry/OpenTelemetry dependencies for proper instrumentation
# These packages are required by @sentry/nextjs for ESM hook registration
# See: https://docs.sentry.io/platforms/javascript/guides/node/troubleshooting
public-hoist-pattern[]=*import-in-the-middle*
public-hoist-pattern[]=*require-in-the-middle*

# Recommended: Also hoist OpenTelemetry packages for consistent resolution
public-hoist-pattern[]=*@opentelemetry*

